Package com.adobe.forms.foundation.usc.model

This package include Unified Storage based model classes.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FormsApplicationContext
    Contract for the model being stored via USC.It contains the minimalistic set of common properties for all use cases across Forms Applications.
    Query
    Querying framework for instance retrieval
    Statement
    Class to add a constraint for querying instances
    StatementGroup
    Class to group various Statement
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AssetSubType
    Enum defines the possible SubTypes for the USC Model being persisted
    AssetType
    Enum defines the possible SubTypes for the USC Model being persisted
    Statement.Operator
    Enum to specify statement operator.
    StatementGroup.JoinOperator
    Enum to specify operator to join with the inner statement.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    USCException
    Common exception being used across USC
